<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cool Dumplings</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-bg-color: #4CAF50; /* Green color for a fresh look */
      --link-color: #fff;
      --link-hover-color: #FFA500; /* Orange hover color for contrast */
      --dropdown-bg-color: #4CAF50;
      --dropdown-box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      --border-radius: 8px;
    }

    nav {
      background-color: var(--primary-bg-color);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      padding: 10px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    li {
      float: left;
    }

    li a {
      display: block;
      color: var(--link-color);
      text-align: center;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    li a:hover {
      background-color: var(--link-hover-color);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    }

    .submenu:hover .dropdown {
      display: block;
    }

    .dropdown {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      background-color: var(--dropdown-bg-color);
      box-shadow: var(--dropdown-box-shadow);
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    }

    .dropdown li {
      float: none;
      display: block;
      text-align: left;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
    }

    section {
      padding: 20px;
      animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in-out;
    }

    section h2 {
      color: var(--primary-bg-color);
      font-size: 2em;
    }

    section img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: var(--border-radius);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    /* Define a fade-in animation */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
      }
      to {
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="#">About</a></li>
      <li class="submenu">
        <a href="#">Menu</a>
        <ul class="dropdown">
          <li><a href="#">Dumpling Types</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Side Dishes</a></li>
          <li><a href="#">Drinks</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="#">Order</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section id="dumplings">
    <h2>Cool Dumplings</h2>
    
    <div class="menu-item">
      <img src="dumpling1.jpg" alt="Dumpling 1">
      <h3>Awesome Dumplings</h3>
      <p>Fresh beef and veggies make these dumplings a flavorful delight.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-item">
      <img src="dumpling2.jpg" alt="Dumpling 2">
      <h3>Veggie Delight</h3>
      <p>Healthy vegetable dumplings with a refreshing taste.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="menu-item">
      <img src="dumpling3.jpg" alt="Dumpling 3">
      <h3>Seafood Sensation</h3>
      <p>Special dumplings with fresh seafood, capturing the essence of the sea.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
